divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: I have tapes of unidentified craft hovering over the eastern Livermore Valley area in California that need to be seen by someone other than the few friends I have shown. (Who have all recommended that I have these tapes seen by professionals who know what they are looking at.)It is due to the serious statements made by my friends who have seen these tapes that have made me finally come forward with them. I am asking that someone please contact me ASAP. This is no hoax or prank, and I believe that I have seen something I was not supposed to have witnessed, let alone tape with my camcorder. Thank you for your time.
